Lenovo to Surpass Apple in Europe PC Sales on Medion

-- B y   R a g n h i l d   K j e t l a n d
-- 
2011-06-01T09:07:54Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-01/lenovo-to-surpass-apple-in-europe-pc-sales-after-medion-deal.html
(Corrects spelling of executive’s name.)  Lenovo Group Ltd. (992) ’s deal to buy
control of German electronics maker  Medion AG (MDN)  will boost the
company’s retail customer business in Western Europe and that
the combined company will surpass  Apple Inc. (AAPL)  in personal
computer sales in Europe, Milko van Duijl, senior vice president
of mature markets, said in a telephone interview from Tokyo. The
transaction will be earnings accretive immediately and is
expected to complete by early September, he said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
